										<li id="comment-73354" class="commentbody"><div class="commenthead"><img alt='ioana`s avatar' src='http://www.ioana75.wordpress.com/avatar.png' class='avatar avatar-32 photo' height='32' width='32' />								<div class="commentcount">22</div>
